following sample generates C4429:  \n  \n```  \n// C4429.cpp  \n// compile with: /W4 /WX  \nint \\ug0e4 = 0;   // C4429  \n// Try the following line instead:  \n// int \\u00e4 = 0;   // OK, a well-formed universal character name.  \n```"}